strings.Value: "That longshank tournament was meh. Goblin holidays are another thing! The last one I visited, they brought a herald of Lamashtu, greatbeast! Ate all guests!"
"I would like to participate. Need to train my aim."
"Pacify your beastling, {name}. I am fed up with the screeches of those talentless bards from the tournament. I need some silence."
"I saw the planes where this kind of "fun" was perceived not as a barbarity but a natural thing. If I had a chance to visit those places again... I would gladly pass on it."
"It would be interesting to witness your holidays! But only from afar, of course, and only from upwind."
"It would be interesting to witness your holidays! But only from afar, of course, and only from upwind."
